    "text": [
        "Dear James,",
        "Hope you are doing great  since we met a few months ago. I'm penning down this letter to make you aware that I switched to another opportunity.",
        "Firstly,Organization, where I worked earlier, was shut down without any prior intimation to us. Also, they didn't pay our salary for the job we performed last 2 months. I was unable to meet my daily needs. However, they provided me with an experience letter with the duties I performed during my tenure in the company. In fact, it helped me to secure a new offer from a reputed company. I'm getting paid double the earlier salary. Moreover, I'm quite excited about this new role and I hope that I get an abroad offer in future. I already have accomplished a few milestones and got a plethora of appreciation from my manager.",
        "Finally , I'm delighted to inform you that I am getting married to Lisa  next summer. Once the date is  confirmed, I'll invite you with a personal invitation card.We are very excited about this new chapter of our life.",
        "I can't wait to see you then.",
        "Cheers,",
        "Priya"
